<html
  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
  xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
  xml:lang="en"
  lang="en"
  dir="ltr"
  metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
  i18n:domain="launchpad"
>

<body>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <h1>Help translate
    <span tal:replace="context/distribution/displayname">foo</span>!</h1>

  <p>
    Are you fluent in a language other than English?
    If so, you can contribute to <span tal:replace="context/title" />
    by translating it with Launchpad&#8217;s 
    <a href="/translations/">Translations</a> software.
    You can translate as much as you like, whenever you like &#8212;
    all you need is a Web browser.
  </p>

  <p>
    To start, <a href="+translate/+login">get a Launchpad account</a>
    if you don&#8217;t already have one.
    Then choose a language below, and start translating.
    It&#8217;s that easy. 
  </p>

  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+potlist" />

</div>
</body>
</html>
 
